    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bat Bots is a retro shooter that brings the feel of 80s arcades right to your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stun the Bats</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stun the latest prototypes of robotic bats that have escaped into the gloomy forest surrounding your secret lab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/c7741a621026cb41bdf6a7f7875c6879.poster.avif?t=1732511196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/c7741a621026cb41bdf6a7f7875c6879.webm?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/c7741a621026cb41bdf6a7f7875c6879.mp4?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Player</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of crosshair designs and colors. Enter your initials to make your mark on the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/95939b014cf3b635b5c228d7fd7aa5e4.poster.avif?t=1732511196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/95939b014cf3b635b5c228d7fd7aa5e4.webm?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/95939b014cf3b635b5c228d7fd7aa5e4.mp4?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stun with Friends and Family</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NOTE: Local Multiplayer Requires At Least One Controller. Multiplayer is NOT supported with ONLY a Mouse &amp; Keyboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with your friends and family as you compete to get the highest score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/0204266a12e5dc367f74b53c35621425.poster.avif?t=1732511196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/0204266a12e5dc367f74b53c35621425.webm?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/0204266a12e5dc367f74b53c35621425.mp4?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or work together to defend your top-secret lab before the Bat Bots escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/2e6ab9cb86cdb8aed2a6710c46cafcf4.poster.avif?t=1732511196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/2e6ab9cb86cdb8aed2a6710c46cafcf4.webm?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/2e6ab9cb86cdb8aed2a6710c46cafcf4.mp4?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Power-Up with Modifiers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your gameplay by shooting the Power Cores dropped by Mod Bats. Once stunned, these cores grant a limited-time modifier that can turn the tide of the game and offer unique advantages in any game mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/0915e68c0fcaea5233524980be20d9de.poster.avif?t=1732511196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/0915e68c0fcaea5233524980be20d9de.webm?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099010/extras/0915e68c0fcaea5233524980be20d9de.mp4?t=1732511196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
